<!doctype html><html lang="ko"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>마이페이지</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/mypage-polish.css"><style>.wrap{max-width:1000px;margin:30px auto;padding:0 18px}.box{border:1px solid #29324f;border-radius:18px;background:#101525;padding:22px;margin-bottom:18px}.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:42px;padding:0 16px;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff3fb4,#10d9ff);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:900}</style></head><body><% const siteBrand=(settings&&settings.brand)?settings.brand:{name:'서비스 디렉터리',showLogo:false,showName:true,logo:'',link:'/'}; %><header class="top"><a class="brand" href="/">홈</a><a class="site-brand-center" href="<%=siteBrand.link||'/'%>">
    <% if(siteBrand.showLogo&&siteBrand.logo){ %><img src="<%=siteBrand.logo%>" alt=""><% } %>
    <% if(siteBrand.showName){ %><span><%=siteBrand.name%></span><% } %>
  </a><nav><a href="/">홈</a><a href="/logout">로그아웃</a></nav></header><main class="wrap"><section class="box"><h2>마이페이지</h2><p>일반회원 페이지입니다. 업체를 운영한다면 업체 등록 신청 후 관리자 승인/연결을 통해 업체회원으로 전환할 수 있습니다.</p><a class="btn" href="/vendor-apply">업체 등록 신청</a></section><section class="box"><h3>찜한 업체</h3><table><tr><th>업체</th><th>지역/업종</th><th>관리</th></tr><% (favorites||[]).forEach(f=>{%><tr><td><a href="/vendor/<%=f.vendor_id%>"><%=f.vendor_name%></a></td><td><%=f.region%> / <%=f.category%></td><td><form method="post" action="/favorite/<%=f.vendor_id%>/delete"><button>찜삭제</button></form></td></tr><%})%></table></section><section class="box"><h3>내 후기</h3><table><tr><th>업체</th><th>제목</th><th>평점</th></tr><% reviews.forEach(r=>{%><tr><td><%=r.vendor_name%></td><td><%=r.title%></td><td>★ <%=r.rating%></td></tr><%})%></table></section></main></body></html>